cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.MM, cs.NE, cs.LG 

The paper deals with the problem of texture image classification, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method involves analyzing the surface morphology of the image, which is related to graphics (cs.GR) and multimedia (cs.MM). The use of Linear Discriminant Analysis for classification suggests a connection to machine learning (cs.NE) and statistical learning (cs.LG).
